{
  "stem": "4695.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I cannot tell what this is in English, But maybe you will help me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN] Polish soldiers and officers, throw away the guns.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You are war prisoners.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then we are war prisoners.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I threw it away because I don't see the beginning from the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't see-- yes, we got to keep [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But we was fighting a little bit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we lost the contact.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we can nothing do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe a week-- maybe a week.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they try to transport us closer to the German territory, because the Polish territory is a large territory.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the capital city was taken fighting, organized fight from the Polish capital city.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- is-- I like to tell you, then Warsaw was staying-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They was staying two weeks, no more.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They was-- that Warsaw was keeping towards the time once it takes-- 23 days, they was fighting.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Even Paris, after 17 days was fallen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But Poland is not so equipped like France, was fighting longer than France.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Yes, after 23, the capital.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- But the trains was no running in Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We-- we walked like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the march closer to the German-- to the Reich, to the German territory.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I will tell you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the second or the third day comes the first selection.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was 16, one behind the other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I cannot see the beginning, maybe 100,000, maybe 150,000 soldiers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they-- [NON-ENGLISH], so they-- to talk--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, to talk loud, to call somebody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How you call this?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When they call-- and they call out to give us a few minutes time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They give us [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This mean, Polish soldiers, [SPEAKING GERMAN], who is from German ancestors, step out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They stepped out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "From the other side comes truck.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
